---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<Layout title="Cyber Liability Insurance | Data Breach Protection | PCFG Insurance" description="Protect your business from cyber threats with cyber liability insurance from PCFG. Coverage for ransomware, data breaches, and cyber attacks. Free quote." keywords="cyber liability insurance, data breach insurance, cybersecurity insurance, ransomware coverage, cyber insurance for small business">
  <Header />
  
  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-gradient-to-br from-red-900 via-navy-900 to-navy-800 text-white">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center">
        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-bold mb-6">Cyber Liability Insurance</h1>
        <p class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-semibold text-red-300 mb-8">Data Breach Protection for the Digital Age</p>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-200 mb-8">
          One data breach. <span class="text-red-400 font-bold">$4.45 million</span> in damages. Could your business survive?
        </p>
        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
          <a href="/commercial-quote" class="bg-red-600 hover:bg-red-700 text-white px-8 py-4 rounded-md font-bold text-lg transition-colors duration-200 inline-block">
            Get a Free Quote
          </a>
          <a href="tel:877-717-7234" class="bg-white/10 hover:bg-white/20 text-white border-2 border-white/30 px-8 py-4 rounded-md font-bold text-lg transition-colors duration-200 inline-block">
            Call (877) 717-7234
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  
  <!-- The Real Cost Section -->
  <section class="py-16 bg-gray-50">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-lg p-8 md:p-12">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">The Real Cost of a Cyber Attack</h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 mb-6">
          A dental practice thought their basic business policy covered cyber attacks. They were wrong. When ransomware hit, they paid $85,000 in ransom, lost $32,000 in revenue during 4 days of downtime, faced HIPAA violations, and spent months rebuilding their reputation.
        </p>
        <div class="bg-red-50 border-l-4 border-red-500 p-6 mb-6">
          <p class="text-2xl font-bold text-red-700">Their "cyber coverage"? A $50,000 sublimit buried in fine print.</p>
          <p class="text-xl text-red-600 mt-2">The gap cost them $197,000 out of pocket.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  
  <!-- Statistics Section -->
  <section class="py-16 bg-navy-900 text-white">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-center mb-12">The Cyber Threat Is Real—and Growing</h2>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        <div class="bg-white/10 backdrop-blur rounded-lg p-6 text-center">
          <p class="text-4xl font-bold text-red-400 mb-2">43%</p>
          <p class="text-gray-200">of cyber attacks target small businesses</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white/10 backdrop-blur rounded-lg p-6 text-center">
          <p class="text-4xl font-bold text-red-400 mb-2">$4.45M</p>
          <p class="text-gray-200">average data breach cost (IBM 2023)</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white/10 backdrop-blur rounded-lg p-6 text-center">
          <p class="text-4xl font-bold text-red-400 mb-2">60%</p>
          <p class="text-gray-200">of small businesses close within 6 months of breach</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white/10 backdrop-blur rounded-lg p-6 text-center">
          <p class="text-4xl font-bold text-red-400 mb-2">300%</p>
          <p class="text-gray-200">increase in ransomware demands YoY</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white/10 backdrop-blur rounded-lg p-6 text-center">
          <p class="text-4xl font-bold text-red-400 mb-2">21 Days</p>
          <p class="text-gray-200">average downtime after attack</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white/10 backdrop-blur rounded-lg p-6 text-center">
          <p class="text-4xl font-bold text-red-400 mb-2">$0</p>
          <p class="text-gray-200">covered by standard business insurance</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  
  <!-- Coverage Section -->
  <section class="py-20">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold text-center text-gray-900 mb-12">What Cyber Liability Insurance Covers</h2>
      
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12">
        <!-- First Party -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-lg p-8">
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-navy-600 mb-6">First-Party Coverage (Your Losses)</h3>
          <ul class="space-y-4">
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <span class="text-green-500 text-xl mr-3">✓</span>
              <div>
                <strong class="text-gray-900">Ransomware & Extortion</strong>
                <p class="text-gray-600">Ransom payments, negotiation, cryptocurrency fees</p>
              </div>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <span class="text-green-500 text-xl mr-3">✓</span>
              <div>
                <strong class="text-gray-900">Data Recovery & Restoration</strong>
                <p class="text-gray-600">IT forensics, data restoration, system rebuilding</p>
              </div>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <span class="text-green-500 text-xl mr-3">✓</span>
              <div>
                <strong class="text-gray-900">Business Interruption</strong>
                <p class="text-gray-600">Lost revenue during downtime, extra expenses</p>
              </div>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <span class="text-green-500 text-xl mr-3">✓</span>
              <div>
                <strong class="text-gray-900">Notification & Credit Monitoring</strong>
                <p class="text-gray-600">Customer notification, credit monitoring services</p>
              </div>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <span class="text-green-500 text-xl mr-3">✓</span>
              <div>
                <strong class="text-gray-900">Crisis Management</strong>
                <p class="text-gray-600">PR firm, crisis communication, reputation management</p>
              </div>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        
        <!-- Third Party -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-lg p-8">
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-navy-600 mb-6">Third-Party Coverage (Liability)</h3>
          <ul class="space-y-4">
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <span class="text-green-500 text-xl mr-3">✓</span>
              <div>
                <strong class="text-gray-900">Privacy Liability</strong>
                <p class="text-gray-600">Defense costs, settlements, regulatory defense</p>
              </div>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <span class="text-green-500 text-xl mr-3">✓</span>
              <div>
                <strong class="text-gray-900">Network Security Liability</strong>
                <p class="text-gray-600">Malware transmission, unauthorized access claims</p>
              </div>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <span class="text-green-500 text-xl mr-3">✓</span>
              <div>
                <strong class="text-gray-900">Media Liability</strong>
                <p class="text-gray-600">Copyright infringement, defamation claims</p>
              </div>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <span class="text-green-500 text-xl mr-3">✓</span>
              <div>
                <strong class="text-gray-900">Regulatory Fines</strong>
                <p class="text-gray-600">HIPAA, PCI DSS, state privacy law violations</p>
              </div>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  
  <!-- Who Needs It -->
  <section class="py-16 bg-gray-50">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-center text-gray-900 mb-12">Who Needs Cyber Liability Insurance?</h2>
      <p class="text-xl text-center text-gray-600 mb-12 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        <strong>Every business that handles sensitive data needs cyber coverage.</strong> If you have a computer and an internet connection, you're at risk.
      </p>
      
      <div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-6">
        <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow p-6 text-center">
          <div class="text-3xl mb-3">🏥</div>
          <p class="font-semibold text-gray-900">Healthcare</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow p-6 text-center">
          <div class="text-3xl mb-3">💰</div>
          <p class="font-semibold text-gray-900">Financial</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow p-6 text-center">
          <div class="text-3xl mb-3">🛒</div>
          <p class="font-semibold text-gray-900">Retail</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow p-6 text-center">
          <div class="text-3xl mb-3">⚖️</div>
          <p class="font-semibold text-gray-900">Professional</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow p-6 text-center">
          <div class="text-3xl mb-3">🏭</div>
          <p class="font-semibold text-gray-900">Manufacturing</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow p-6 text-center">
          <div class="text-3xl mb-3">🎓</div>
          <p class="font-semibold text-gray-900">Education</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow p-6 text-center">
          <div class="text-3xl mb-3">❤️</div>
          <p class="font-semibold text-gray-900">Nonprofits</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow p-6 text-center">
          <div class="text-3xl mb-3">👥</div>
          <p class="font-semibold text-gray-900">Any Business</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  
  <!-- Real World Scenarios -->
  <section class="py-20">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-center text-gray-900 mb-12">Real-World Cyber Attack Scenarios</h2>
      
      <div class="space-y-12">
        <!-- Scenario 1 -->
        <div class="bg-red-50 rounded-lg p-8 border-l-4 border-red-500">
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-red-900 mb-4">The Ransomware Nightmare</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
            A 50-employee manufacturer clicked on a phishing email. Within hours, ransomware encrypted their entire network—including backups. The attackers demanded $250,000 in Bitcoin.
          </p>
          <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 mt-6">
            <div class="bg-white rounded p-4">
              <p class="font-bold text-red-600 mb-2">Without Cyber Insurance:</p>
              <p class="text-gray-600">Paid ransom + $75K recovery + $400K lost revenue. Nearly bankrupted.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-white rounded p-4">
              <p class="font-bold text-green-600 mb-2">With Cyber Insurance:</p>
              <p class="text-gray-600">Ransom covered, forensics paid, business interruption covered. Paid only deductible.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <!-- Scenario 2 -->
        <div class="bg-red-50 rounded-lg p-8 border-l-4 border-red-500">
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-red-900 mb-4">The Data Breach Lawsuit</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
            A medical practice's patient database was accessed. 8,000 records exposed. Required notification and credit monitoring by law.
          </p>
          <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 mt-6">
            <div class="bg-white rounded p-4">
              <p class="font-bold text-red-600 mb-2">Without Cyber Insurance:</p>
              <p class="text-gray-600">$180K notification + $120K monitoring + $400K lawsuit + $50K HIPAA fines = $750K+</p>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-white rounded p-4">
              <p class="font-bold text-green-600 mb-2">With Cyber Insurance:</p>
              <p class="text-gray-600">All costs covered. Crisis management handled. Practice survived.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  
  <!-- Why PCFG -->
  <section class="py-16 bg-navy-800 text-white">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-center mb-12">Why Choose PCFG for Cyber Insurance?</h2>
      
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="text-4xl mb-4">🛡️</div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">Expertise in Cyber Risk</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-300">We work with carriers who specialize in cyber coverage—not just add it as an afterthought.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="text-4xl mb-4">🔍</div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">Pre-Breach Services</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-300">Risk assessments, employee training, incident response planning, vulnerability scanning.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="text-4xl mb-4">🚨</div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">Post-Breach Response</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-300">24/7 breach hotline, pre-vetted forensics, experienced breach counsel, crisis communication.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  
  <!-- Cost Section -->
  <section class="py-16 bg-gray-50">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-center text-gray-900 mb-8">Understanding Cyber Insurance Costs</h2>
      
      <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-lg p-8 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 mb-6">Typical annual premiums based on business size:</p>
        
        <div class="space-y-4 mb-8">
          <div class="flex justify-between items-center border-b pb-3">
            <span class="text-gray-700">Small business ($1M revenue)</span>
            <span class="font-bold text-navy-600">$1,500 - $3,000/year</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flex justify-between items-center border-b pb-3">
            <span class="text-gray-700">Mid-size ($10M revenue)</span>
            <span class="font-bold text-navy-600">$5,000 - $15,000/year</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flex justify-between items-center">
            <span class="text-gray-700">Average breach cost without insurance</span>
            <span class="font-bold text-red-600">$4.45 million</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="bg-red-50 border-l-4 border-red-500 p-4">
          <p class="text-red-800 font-semibold">The investment is minimal compared to the potential loss.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  
  <!-- CTA Section -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-gradient-to-br from-red-900 to-navy-900 text-white">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
      <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-6">Don't Wait for the Ransom Note</h2>
      <p class="text-xl text-gray-200 mb-8">
        Every day without cyber coverage is a day you're gambling with your business's survival. The 60% of small businesses that close after a breach all thought "it won't happen to me."
      </p>
      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
        <a href="/commercial-quote" class="bg-red-600 hover:bg-red-700 text-white px-8 py-4 rounded-md font-bold text-lg transition-colors duration-200 inline-block">
          Get Your Free Quote
        </a>
        <a href="tel:877-717-7234" class="bg-white/10 hover:bg-white/20 text-white border-2 border-white/30 px-8 py-4 rounded-md font-bold text-lg transition-colors duration-200 inline-block">
          Call (877) 717-7234
        </a>
      </div>
      <p class="mt-8 text-gray-300">
        Our cyber specialists will assess your exposure and design coverage that actually protects you.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>
  
  <Footer />
</Layout>
